text: Well maintained condominium equipped with surveillance cameras and virtual security systems. Cleanliness is top notch. It has amenities such as gymnasium room, basement car park, playground, barbecue area and a swimming pool. Nearest bus stop is only 5-7 mins walk away, which can take you to the nearest MRT station, Tanah Merah. Besides, Cold Storage, 7-Eleven, medical and dental clinics is just few steps away from the condo.
Upcoming next to new upcoming Mrt station,Sungei Bedok TE31/DT37.It will connect city easier around the vicinity.
Convenient next door to bedok ria MRT
